      <title>Exploring the Beauty of Nepal</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/post/nepal-travel/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/post/nepal-travel/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Nepal — The Land of Himalayas&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;nepal--the-land-of-himalayas&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#nepal--the-land-of-himalayas&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Nepal is home to 8 of the world&amp;rsquo;s 14 highest peaks including &lt;strong&gt;Mount Everest&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Must Visit Places&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;must-visit-places&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span&#xD;&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#must-visit-places&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🏔️ Pokhara — City of lakes and mountains&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🛕 Kathmandu — Historic temples and culture&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;🦏 Chitwan — Wildlife and nature&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Stay tuned for detailed travel guides!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
